### 3-4. Chat / Message 도메인 (`catalog = "chat"`)

**파일 경로:** `domain/src/main/kotlin/com/maum/backend/entity/chat/`

```kotlin
// ChatRoomEntity.kt
@Entity
@Table(catalog = "chat", name = "chat_room")
class ChatRoomEntity(
    @Id
    @GeneratedValue(generator = "uuid2")
    @GenericGenerator(name = "uuid2", strategy = "uuid2")
    val id: String = "",

    @Column(nullable = false)
    val user1Id: String,

    @Column(nullable = false)
    val user2Id: String,

    val matchId: String? = null,

    @Column(nullable = false)
    var status: Int = ChatRoomStatus.ACTIVE.value, // 0:ACTIVE, 1:CLOSED

    var lastMessageAt: LocalDateTime? = null,

    @CreatedDate
    @Column(columnDefinition = "datetime(3)", nullable = false, updatable = false)
    var createdAt: LocalDateTime = LocalDateTime.now(),

    @LastModifiedDate
    var updatedAt: LocalDateTime = LocalDateTime.now(),
) {
    enum class ChatRoomStatus(val value: Int) {
        ACTIVE(0), CLOSED(1);
        companion object { fun fromValue(v: Int) = entries.first { it.value == v } }
    }
}
```

> **메시지 저장소**: 채팅 메시지는 대용량/고속 쓰기 특성상 **DynamoDB**에 저장합니다. JPA Entity 대신 DynamoDB 문서 모델을 사용합니다.

```kotlin
// ChatMessageDocument.kt (DynamoDB)
// PK: roomId#yyyyMMdd  SK: timestamp#messageId
data class ChatMessageDocument(
    val roomId: String,
    val messageId: String,
    val senderId: String,
    val content: String,
    val messageType: String,    // "TEXT" | "IMAGE" | "VOICE_NOTE"
    val sentAt: String,         // ISO 8601
    val readAt: String? = null,
    val deletedAt: String? = null,
)
```

### 3-5. Follow / Block (`catalog = "maum"`)

```kotlin
// FollowEntity.kt
@Entity
@Table(catalog = "maum", name = "follow")
class FollowEntity(
    @Id
    @GeneratedValue(generator = "uuid2")
