## 4. GraphQL 스키마 설계

**파일 경로:** `graphql/src/main/resources/graphql/`

### 4-1. schema.graphqls (루트)

```graphql
type Query
type Mutation
```

### 4-2. user.graphqls

```graphql
type User {
    id: ID!
    nickname: String!
    gender: String!
    birthYear: Int!
    bio: String
    profileImageUrl: String
    mannerScore: Int!
    status: String!
    createdAt: String!
}

type SimpleUser {
    id: ID!
    nickname: String!
    profileImageUrl: String
    mannerScore: Int!
}

input RegisterUserInput {
    phoneNumber: String!
    nickname: String!
    gender: String!
    birthYear: Int!
}

input UpdateUserProfileInput {
    nickname: String
    bio: String
    profileImageUrl: String
}

extend type Query {
    me: User!
    user(userId: ID!): User
}

extend type Mutation {
    registerUser(input: RegisterUserInput!): User!
    updateUserProfile(input: UpdateUserProfileInput!): User!
    deleteAccount: Boolean!
}
```

### 4-3. match.graphqls

```graphql
type Match {
    id: ID!
    requester: SimpleUser!
    receiver: SimpleUser!
    status: String!          # PENDING | ACCEPTED | REJECTED | EXPIRED
    createdAt: String!
    acceptedAt: String
}

input SendMatchRequestInput {
    receiverId: ID!
}

extend type Query {
    myMatches(status: String, limit: Int, offset: Int): [Match!]!
    match(matchId: ID!): Match
}

extend type Mutation {
    sendMatchRequest(input: SendMatchRequestInput!): Match!
    acceptMatch(matchId: ID!): Match!
    rejectMatch(matchId: ID!): Match!
}
```

### 4-4. call.graphqls

```graphql
type Call {
    id: ID!
    caller: SimpleUser!
    receiver: SimpleUser!
    status: String!          # RINGING | CONNECTED | ENDED | MISSED | DECLINED
    callType: String!        # VOICE | VIDEO
    durationSeconds: Int!
    startedAt: String
    endedAt: String
    createdAt: String!
}

type CallReview {
    id: ID!
    callId: ID!
    reviewer: SimpleUser!
    reviewee: SimpleUser!
    score: Int!
    comment: String
    createdAt: String!
}

input InitiateCallInput {
    receiverId: ID!
    callType: String!
}

input SubmitCallReviewInput {
    callId: ID!
    revieweeId: ID!
    score: Int!
    comment: String
}

extend type Query {
    callHistory(limit: Int, offset: Int): [Call!]!
    call(callId: ID!): Call
}

extend type Mutation {
    initiateCall(input: InitiateCallInput!): Call!
    endCall(callId: ID!): Call!
    submitCallReview(input: SubmitCallReviewInput!): CallReview!
}
```

### 4-5. chat.graphqls

```graphql
type ChatRoom {
    id: ID!
    partner: SimpleUser!
    lastMessage: ChatMessage
    lastMessageAt: String
    createdAt: String!
}

type ChatMessage {
    id: ID!
    roomId: ID!
    sender: SimpleUser!
    content: String!
    messageType: String!     # TEXT | IMAGE | VOICE_NOTE
    sentAt: String!
    readAt: String
}

input SendMessageInput {
    roomId: ID!
    content: String!
    messageType: String!
}

extend type Query {
    myChatRooms(limit: Int, offset: Int): [ChatRoom!]!
    chatMessages(roomId: ID!, limit: Int, lastMessageId: ID): [ChatMessage!]!
}

extend type Mutation {
    sendMessage(input: SendMessageInput!): ChatMessage!
    markMessagesRead(roomId: ID!): Boolean!
}
```

---

## 5. gRPC Proto 설계

**파일 경로:** `protobuf/src/main/proto/{domain}/`

### 5-1. user/user_service.proto

```protobuf
syntax = "proto3";
package user;

option java_multiple_files = true;
option java_package = "com.maum.backend.protobuf.user";

service UserService {
  rpc GetUser(GetUserRequest) returns (GetUserResponse);
  rpc GetMe(GetMeRequest) returns (GetUserResponse);
  rpc RegisterUser(RegisterUserRequest) returns (RegisterUserResponse);
  rpc UpdateUserProfile(UpdateUserProfileRequest) returns (UpdateUserProfileResponse);
  rpc DeleteUser(DeleteUserRequest) returns (DeleteUserResponse);
}

message UserProfile {
  string id = 1;
  string nickname = 2;
  string gender = 3;
  int32 birth_year = 4;
  string bio = 5;
  string profile_image_url = 6;
  int32 manner_score = 7;
  string status = 8;
  string created_at = 9;
}

message GetUserRequest { string user_id = 1; }
message GetMeRequest   { string user_id = 1; }
message GetUserResponse { UserProfile user = 1; }

message RegisterUserRequest {
  string phone_number = 1;
  string nickname = 2;
  string gender = 3;
  int32 birth_year = 4;
}
message RegisterUserResponse { UserProfile user = 1; }

message UpdateUserProfileRequest {
  string user_id = 1;
  optional string nickname = 2;
  optional string bio = 3;
  optional string profile_image_url = 4;
}
message UpdateUserProfileResponse { UserProfile user = 1; }

message DeleteUserRequest  { string user_id = 1; }
message DeleteUserResponse { bool success = 1; }
```

### 5-2. match/match_service.proto

```protobuf
syntax = "proto3";
package match;

option java_multiple_files = true;
option java_package = "com.maum.backend.protobuf.match";

service MatchService {
  rpc SendMatchRequest(SendMatchRequestRequest) returns (SendMatchRequestResponse);
  rpc AcceptMatch(AcceptMatchRequest) returns (AcceptMatchResponse);
  rpc RejectMatch(RejectMatchRequest) returns (RejectMatchResponse);
  rpc GetMatch(GetMatchRequest) returns (GetMatchResponse);
  rpc ListMatches(ListMatchesRequest) returns (ListMatchesResponse);
}

message Match {
  string id = 1;
  string requester_id = 2;
  string receiver_id = 3;
  string status = 4;
  string created_at = 5;
  optional string accepted_at = 6;
}

message SendMatchRequestRequest {
  string requester_id = 1;
  string receiver_id = 2;
}
message SendMatchRequestResponse { Match match = 1; }

message AcceptMatchRequest { string user_id = 1; string match_id = 2; }
message AcceptMatchResponse { Match match = 1; }

message RejectMatchRequest { string user_id = 1; string match_id = 2; }
message RejectMatchResponse { Match match = 1; }

message GetMatchRequest { string user_id = 1; string match_id = 2; }
message GetMatchResponse { Match match = 1; }

message ListMatchesRequest {
  string user_id = 1;
  optional string status = 2;
  int32 limit = 3;
  int32 offset = 4;
}
message ListMatchesResponse { repeated Match matches = 1; }
```

### 5-3. call/call_service.proto

```protobuf
syntax = "proto3";
package call;

option java_multiple_files = true;
option java_package = "com.maum.backend.protobuf.call";

service CallService {
  rpc InitiateCall(InitiateCallRequest) returns (InitiateCallResponse);
  rpc EndCall(EndCallRequest) returns (EndCallResponse);
  rpc GetCall(GetCallRequest) returns (GetCallResponse);
  rpc ListCallHistory(ListCallHistoryRequest) returns (ListCallHistoryResponse);
  rpc SubmitCallReview(SubmitCallReviewRequest) returns (SubmitCallReviewResponse);
  rpc GetMannerScore(GetMannerScoreRequest) returns (GetMannerScoreResponse);
}

message Call {
  string id = 1;
  string caller_id = 2;
  string receiver_id = 3;
  string status = 4;
  string call_type = 5;
  int32 duration_seconds = 6;
  optional string started_at = 7;
  optional string ended_at = 8;
  string created_at = 9;
}

message CallReview {
  string id = 1;
  string call_id = 2;
  string reviewer_id = 3;
  string reviewee_id = 4;
  int32 score = 5;
  optional string comment = 6;
  string created_at = 7;
}

message InitiateCallRequest {
  string caller_id = 1;
  string receiver_id = 2;
  string call_type = 3;
}
message InitiateCallResponse { Call call = 1; }

message EndCallRequest { string user_id = 1; string call_id = 2; }
message EndCallResponse { Call call = 1; }

message GetCallRequest { string user_id = 1; string call_id = 2; }
message GetCallResponse { Call call = 1; }

message ListCallHistoryRequest {
  string user_id = 1;
  int32 limit = 2;
  int32 offset = 3;
}
message ListCallHistoryResponse { repeated Call calls = 1; }

message SubmitCallReviewRequest {
  string reviewer_id = 1;
  string call_id = 2;
  string reviewee_id = 3;
  int32 score = 4;
  optional string comment = 5;
}
message SubmitCallReviewResponse { CallReview review = 1; }

message GetMannerScoreRequest { string user_id = 1; }
message GetMannerScoreResponse { int32 manner_score = 1; }
```

### 5-4. chat/chat_service.proto

```protobuf
syntax = "proto3";
package chat;

option java_multiple_files = true;
option java_package = "com.maum.backend.protobuf.chat";

service ChatService {
  rpc ListChatRooms(ListChatRoomsRequest) returns (ListChatRoomsResponse);
  rpc ListChatMessages(ListChatMessagesRequest) returns (ListChatMessagesResponse);
  rpc SendMessage(SendMessageRequest) returns (SendMessageResponse);
  rpc MarkMessagesRead(MarkMessagesReadRequest) returns (MarkMessagesReadResponse);
}

message ChatRoom {
  string id = 1;
  string user1_id = 2;
  string user2_id = 3;
  optional string last_message_at = 4;
  string created_at = 5;
}

message ChatMessage {
  string id = 1;
  string room_id = 2;
  string sender_id = 3;
  string content = 4;
  string message_type = 5;
  string sent_at = 6;
  optional string read_at = 7;
}

message ListChatRoomsRequest { string user_id = 1; int32 limit = 2; int32 offset = 3; }
message ListChatRoomsResponse { repeated ChatRoom rooms = 1; }

message ListChatMessagesRequest {
  string user_id = 1;
  string room_id = 2;
  int32 limit = 3;
  optional string last_message_id = 4;
}
message ListChatMessagesResponse { repeated ChatMessage messages = 1; }

message SendMessageRequest {
  string sender_id = 1;
  string room_id = 2;
  string content = 3;
  string message_type = 4;
}
message SendMessageResponse { ChatMessage message = 1; }

message MarkMessagesReadRequest { string user_id = 1; string room_id = 2; }
message MarkMessagesReadResponse { bool success = 1; }
```

---

## 6. 영향 범위 및 구현 위치 정리

| 도메인 | GraphQL Controller | gRPC Service (서버) | Repository |
|--------|-------------------|---------------------|------------|
| User | `graphql/controller/user/UserController.kt` | `user-service/controller/UserGrpcService.kt` | `domain/repository/user/UserRepository.kt`, `UserProfileRepository.kt` |
| Match | `graphql/controller/match/MatchController.kt` | `match-service/controller/MatchGrpcService.kt` | `domain/repository/match/MatchRepository.kt` |
| Call | `graphql/controller/call/CallController.kt` | `call-service/controller/CallGrpcService.kt` | `domain/repository/call/CallRepository.kt`, `CallReviewRepository.kt` |
| Chat | `graphql/controller/chat/ChatController.kt` | `chat-service/controller/ChatGrpcService.kt` | `domain/repository/chat/ChatRoomRepository.kt` + DynamoDB |

---

## 7. 설계 결정 사항 요약

**MySQL (JPA Entity) 저장 대상:**
- `maum` 카탈로그: `user`, `user_profile`, `match`, `call`, `call_review`, `follow`, `block`
- `chat` 카탈로그: `chat_room` (메타데이터 전용)
- `notification` 카탈로그: `notification`, `notification_setting`

**DynamoDB 저장 대상:**
- 채팅 메시지 (`ChatMessageDocument`) — 고속 쓰기, 시계열 조회 특성

**Redis 캐싱 대상:**
- `UserProfile` (프로필 조회 빈도 높음)
- `MannerScore` (통화 후 업데이트, 실시간 조회 필요)
- 온라인 상태 (Call 연결 전 수신자 상태 확인)

**Nullable 설계 원칙:**
- GraphQL: 필수 식별자/상태는 `!`, 선택적 상세 정보는 nullable
- Proto: 선택 필드에 `optional` 명시
- Entity: 비즈니스 핵심 필드는 `nullable = false`, 이력 타임스탬프는 nullable

